1
00:00:01,420 --> 00:00:02,660
It happened again.

2
00:00:02,740 --> 00:00:04,580
Somebody died in the Lava-Matic.

3
00:00:05,140 --> 00:00:06,840
I saw it like I was there.

4
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:10,420
Agatha's dead, so who's gonna tell me
what's going on?

5
00:00:25,010 --> 00:00:26,120
Put your hands in the air!

6
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:30,740
Damn, the police.

7
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:32,360
They already found me.

8
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:35,510
I'll spend the rest of
my days rotting in prison,

9
00:00:35,511 --> 00:00:37,520
and I'll never find out
what really happened.

10
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:40,640
No, it's not gonna happen like that.

